Based in Portugal, Wire IT is your specialized IT consulting partner with 18 years of experience driven by an experienced and senior team that helps clients make the right decisions in a fast-moving market.

Wire IT's ambition is to grow while keeping true to its nature: agile, people-centered, and fun.

As we like to say: Its not only what we do, its how we manage that truly make the difference.

If you're looking for more than just a job - if you're looking for a place where you can truly make a difference - you might be the next person to join WIRE IT.

Role: AI Quality Assurance Engineer

Location: Hybrid, Porto

Required Skills

Minimum 3 years of experience testing backend or middleware applications, preferably within banking or brokerage systems

Hands-on experience with AI testing tools for automated test generation, anomaly detection, and failure prediction

Strong expertise in root cause analysis, including log analysis, diagnostic tools, and collaboration with development teams

Proficiency in Linux environments, including shell commands, scripting, and process troubleshooting

Proven ability to design and execute comprehensive integration test plans and automated regression strategies

Experience validating AI components and applying machine learning models to optimize testing coverage

Strong communication skills for documenting defects, producing risk assessments, and mentoring teams on AI-powered testing practices

We Offer

No-term full-time contract;

Health Insurance;

22 days of paid vacation;

4 extra days annually (Carnival, Christmas Eve, New Year's Eve, Birthday);

Meal Allowance on card (Coverflex);

Referral Bonus;

Special discounts and flex options;

Training annual budget;

A great team-oriented culture;

Chance to become a part of a dynamically growing international company;

Challenging projects giving the unique opportunity to grow and learn.

